latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The long awaited moisturizer is here. This lightweight no frill moisturizer /hydrator keeps your skin deeply hydrated all day long and can be used by All Skin Types including acne and Malassezia aka fungal acne prone skin (yes you heard that right).

This moisturizer does not contain oils, fatty acids, fatty esters, fatty alcohols, lecithin, polysorbates, PEGs (basically everything you look to avoid if your skin is prone to Malassezia). It creates a veil of hydration and makes your skin super smooth. Multi-molecular hyaluronic acids work together to help maintain skin’s hydration level and strengthen skin’s moisture barrier creating a healthy looking balanced complexion perfect for your no makeup days or for creating a hydrated makeup base.
